State Regulations

The following forms shall be used in conjunction with the
administration of article 46 of the Vehicle and Traffic Law. The instructions
on all forms must be followed and all forms must be appropriately completed in
order to be accepted. Notice of lien (Form MV-900). Printed by lender in the
following size and format. Size 81/2 inches by 51/2 inches. Image
